y. The practical approach right now is still using API keys as secrets, but trusted publishing with OIDC is the more secure direction I should recommend.","outputTokens":2416,"requestId":"6C4C:B0194:D4D46C:1094CC9:6A012A33"},"id":"4052edde-a4c9-409e-936a-5090ef834b72","timestamp":"2026-05-11T01:01:24.559Z","parentId":"c21b8b73-38ff-483f-90d8-c9ce4e05d855"}
